features: Minimalist Grid Style： An exemplar representation of fashion-forward design, the contemporary inspired patterns leave a sophisticated and refined impression that is highly versatile.
Machine Washable Area Rug: Designed with your convenience in mind, our rug is machine washable, ensuring easy cleaning and maintenance. Simply toss it in the washing machine for hassle-free care.

Non-slip Backing: The living room rug is made of TPR non-slip rubber backing, which helps to keep the rug in place, prevents heavy traffic from scuffing the floor. Even if running on it quickly, it not moves and slides around.

Soft Throw Rugs: Walk on a soft Modern carpet and have a good mood! Our indoor living room rug made of faux wool, if you walking barefoot on the bedroom carpet, you will have the feeling of stepping on clouds, creating a comfortable and safe area for your children and family!

Care and Maintenance: Upon receiving the rug, please unfold it. Initially, there may be creases, but worry not. These creases can be effectively removed by rolling the rug up from any corners (with the patterned side facing outward) and allowing it to sit for one or two days or by ironing the back side.
